long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This feature is now natively available in Jumpcloud website at console.jumpcloud.com, so this plugin is now redundant.
Leaving this plugin on for posterity.

Adds a search box to filter applications on console.jumpcloud.com
Provides a much needed search functionality when you have multiple apps rather than using browser based search only.
